---
const { className = "", style = "" } = Astro.props;
---

<p class={`thumb-border-legend ${className}`.trim()} style={style}>
  Rainbow borders indicate published S-tier games. Gold borders indicate games with reviews.
  Purple borders indicate games with walkthroughs. Silver borders indicate Completed status.
  Blue borders indicate In Progress status. Orange borders indicate On Hold status.
  Red borders indicate Did Not Finish status. Dark green borders indicate Waiting For Update status.
</p>

<style>
  .thumb-border-legend{
    opacity:.75;
    margin:.5rem 0 1rem;
  }
</style>
